262
00:49:23.399 --> 00:49:25.026
you'll be trapped in the corridors.

263
00:49:25.193 --> 00:49:28.488
There's no escape route.
No passage you can take.

264
00:49:28.655 --> 00:49:32.825
If you make it. it will be
the same way you came.

265
00:49:32.992 --> 00:49:35.119
You have to break your way out.

266
00:49:36.537 --> 00:49:38.623
You should be careful.

267
00:49:38.790 --> 00:49:41.668
You're not here to do good.

268
00:49:41.834 --> 00:49:43.002
Don't be blind.

269
00:49:43.169 --> 00:49:45.922
I've seen that old man here before.

270
00:49:46.089 --> 00:49:49.509
He knows this building
as well as I do.

271
00:49:50.468 --> 00:49:52.178
Not every cop
is swayed by money. sir.

272
00:49:52.345 --> 00:49:57.267
If I believed that. I would
never have opened the door.

273
00:50:09.904 --> 00:50:12.365
He's boneheaded and stubborn.

274
00:50:13.199 --> 00:50:15.118
But he's a good man.

275
00:50:15.910 --> 00:50:20.248
Take care of him.
I'll be back as soon as I can.

276
00:50:56.617 --> 00:50:58.911
Man. that's too much!

277
00:51:03.791 --> 00:51:05.668
He's here!

278
00:51:35.531 --> 00:51:37.116
Up!

279
00:52:56.195 --> 00:52:57.989
Take the leg!

280
00:56:03.716 --> 00:56:06.052
Where'd he come from?

281
00:57:12.618 --> 00:57:15.121
Stop it! Calm down!

282
00:57:20.209 --> 00:57:22.128
What the fuck are you doing here?

283
00:57:35.391 --> 00:57:37.059
Keep watch.

284
00:57:57.913 --> 00:57:59.331
They're gone.

285
00:58:01.667 --> 00:58:03.586
We don't know that yet.

286
00:58:05.004 --> 00:58:10.509
Think about it. Jaka.
one's a cripple. the other a rookie.

287
00:58:10.676 --> 00:58:12.553
They didn't stand a chance.

288
00:58:12.970 --> 00:58:17.433
Now. I'm sorry. but we're not going
up there just to find their dead bodies.

289
00:58:21.020 --> 00:58:22.730
Listen to me. you prick.

290
00:58:22.897 --> 00:58:27.485
When it comes to the lives of my men.
it'd be wise for you to shut the fuck up.

291
00:58:27.818 --> 00:58:30.070
You wanna talk about risking lives?

292
00:58:30.237 --> 00:58:32.364
Well. you already risked theirs.

293
00:58:33.324 --> 00:58:35.242
And now I own yours.

294
00:58:35.785 --> 00:58:36.911
Who ordered this?

295
00:58:37.077 --> 00:58:38.621
What?

296
00:58:38.788 --> 00:58:40.498
Well. it sure as shit wasn't you.

297
00:58:40.664 --> 00:58:44.877
No one leads the charge when
it comes to their own dirty work.

298
00:58:46.295 --> 00:58:48.130
Careful. Jaka.

299
00:58:48.464 --> 00:58:50.299
Remember your rank.

300
00:58:50.466 --> 00:58:51.509
Rank?

301
00:58:51.675 --> 00:58:53.761
Rank counts for shit now.

302
00:58:53.928 --> 00:58:55.888
Once we make it out of here

303
00:58:56.055 --> 00:59:00.810
you'll be mopping up puddles of piss
in a prison cell for the rest of your life.

304
00:59:00.976 --> 00:59:04.146
We're not here to do good.

305
00:59:04.396 --> 00:59:07.608
We're here to make someone rich.

306
00:59:08.192 --> 00:59:12.780
I'm asking you one last time.
who ordered this hit?

307
00:59:15.115 --> 00:59:19.703
Another time maybe.
I'll take my chances here first.

308
00:59:24.416 --> 00:59:26.126
Suit yourself.

309
00:59:28.295 --> 00:59:33.008
We're going back up there.
We're going to find them.

310
00:59:33.384 --> 00:59:36.053
And only then do we leave.

311
00:59:37.471 --> 00:59:38.848
Any objections?

312
00:59:42.393 --> 00:59:44.061
Thought not.

313
00:59:45.062 --> 00:59:46.897
Everyone ready.

314
00:59:49.733 --> 00:59:51.360
Move.

315
01:00:16.093 --> 01:00:17.261
Protect him!

316
01:00:17.803 --> 01:00:19.346
Now!

317
01:01:48.310 --> 01:01:50.604
I've never really liked using these.

318
01:01:54.274 --> 01:01:56.068
Takes away the rush.

319
01:01:58.946 --> 01:02:01.073
Squeezing a trigger.

320
01:02:01.448 --> 01:02:03.951
it's like ordering takeout.

321
01:02:04.535 --> 01:02:06.328
Now this.

322
01:02:07.830 --> 01:02:09.873
This is the thing.

323
01:02:11.625 --> 01:02:13.752
This is the pulse.

324
01:02:16.005 --> 01:02:18.298
This is what I do.

325
01:05:18.103 --> 01:05:20.314
You shouldn't be here.

326
01:05:22.733 --> 01:05:25.652
Nor should you.

327
01:05:30.657 --> 01:05:31.867
Who are they?

328
01:05:38.040 --> 01:05:39.833
They're no one.

329
01:05:46.215 --> 01:05:48.467
Don't they check for links
before they send you?

330
01:05:48.634 --> 01:05:52.971
They got nothing on record
about you. just your first name.

331
01:05:53.222 --> 01:05:55.307
No one knows shit about us.

332
01:05:57.559 --> 01:06:00.896
I almost fucking choked when they
pinned your photo on the board.

333
01:06:01.480 --> 01:06:04.566
Six years with no contact.
and this is how I find you.

334
01:06:10.739 --> 01:06:13.033
You have to leave this place.

335
01:06:13.825 --> 01:06:15.285
Now.

336
01:06:15.869 --> 01:06:17.454
I can't.

337
01:06:17.871 --> 01:06:19.081
Not without my team.

338
01:06:19.248 --> 01:06:21.500
What?
You heard me.

339
01:06:21.667 --> 01:06:23.961
I don't think you realize
the situation you're in.

340
01:06:24.127 --> 01:06:27.464
Oh. I understand fine.
I'm not the one living here.

341
01:06:28.715 --> 01:06:30.634
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

342
01:06:30.801 --> 01:06:33.804
Next time you want to talk.
just pick up the phone.

343
01:06:33.971 --> 01:06:37.599
I spent the last 24 hours listening to
my best friends talk about killing you.

344
01:06:37.766 --> 01:06:40.143
I'm the only one who can get
you out of here safely.

345
01:06:40.310 --> 01:06:41.979
Without handcuffs
around your wrists.

346
01:06:42.145 --> 01:06:44.106
Wait. what's that?

347
01:06:44.273 --> 01:06:46.358
You're getting me out?

348
01:06:46.525 --> 01:06:49.903
You need saving. Last I checked my
guys are almost done collecting these.

349
01:06:50.070 --> 01:06:53.365
Fuck you. just do what I say.
And go where? Home?

350
01:06:55.659 --> 01:06:58.578
If I was such a disappointment
to him then...

351
01:07:01.707 --> 01:07:04.626
think how proud he's gonna be
now that I am who I am.

352
01:07:06.962 --> 01:07:11.300
He just wants you home.
we all do.

353
01:07:16.847 --> 01:07:18.890
You don't get it.

354
01:07:20.642 --> 01:07:24.271
That ain't me any more. This is.

355
01:07:25.063 --> 01:07:29.693
Just because you see what I do as
wrong doesn't mean I can't be good at it.

356
01:07:29.860 --> 01:07:31.653
This is the one thing
I know how to do.

357
01:07:31.820 --> 01:07:33.905
I fucking own it.

358
01:07:35.240 --> 01:07:36.825
No. Rama.

359
01:07:38.035 --> 01:07:40.704
I won't go back to who I was.

360
01:07:52.716 --> 01:07:54.301
You're going to be an uncle.

361
01:07:58.597 --> 01:08:00.015
What?

362
01:08:01.308 --> 01:08:04.186
Yeah. a boy. due in two months.

363
01:08:12.903 --> 01:08:16.907
You tell me this now.
because you expect me to leave.

364
01:08:17.074 --> 01:08:19.117
I told you because
you're my fucking brother.

365
01:08:19.284 --> 01:08:21.078
Think about what you're doing!

366
01:08:21.244 --> 01:08:24.498
If you stay here you'll be fucking
dead before that boy is born.

367
01:08:24.664 --> 01:08:26.124
Haven't you thought about that?

368
01:08:26.291 --> 01:08:29.586
I've thought about it every day
since I was given this assignment.

369
01:08:29.753 --> 01:08:31.630
And it fucking terrifies me.

370
01:08:33.548 --> 01:08:36.343
This is fucking ridiculous.

371
01:08:43.517 --> 01:08:45.602
You should leave.
I don't have much time.

372
01:08:46.895 --> 01:08:49.731
At least change your clothing
before you go back out there.

373
01:08:51.942 --> 01:08:54.694
No. this fits me just fine.

374
01:09:02.244 --> 01:09:09.126
Hang back. till the area is clear.

375
01:09:28.478 --> 01:09:31.106
Wait! Hold the lift.

376
01:09:41.825 --> 01:09:45.078
Where are your men?
Still hunting.

377
01:09:45.245 --> 01:09:48.081
And yours?
Same.

378
01:09:49.207 --> 01:09:52.377
Where are you taking him?
The boss.

379
01:10:02.429 --> 01:10:03.889
That's not the guy.

380
01:10:05.015 --> 01:10:07.726
It is.
No. it definitely isn't.

381
01:10:07.893 --> 01:10:09.895
Plus this guy is dead already.

382
01:10:10.187 --> 01:10:12.397
Yeah. well. I'm taking him anyway.

383
01:10:13.315 --> 01:10:15.108
What have you got?

384
01:11:10.830 --> 01:11:12.082
Rama.

385
01:11:12.249 --> 01:11:13.667
Get in.

386
01:11:22.676 --> 01:11:24.177
Where's Bowo?

387
01:11:24.344 --> 01:11:25.971
He's safe.

388
01:11:27.180 --> 01:11:31.685
We lost the sergeant.
They got him. he's dead.

389
01:11:33.395 --> 01:11:36.523
Motherfucker dragged him
across the floor like an animal.

390
01:11:37.649 --> 01:11:40.902
What happened?
Why did you split up?

391
01:11:41.069 --> 01:11:44.406
We were ambushed. outnumbered.

392
01:11:44.573 --> 01:11:46.366
And he ran.

393
01:11:46.992 --> 01:11:49.327
Sergeant ordered me to protect him.

394
01:11:51.204 --> 01:11:55.625
Right now all we can do
is try to survive this.

395
01:11:55.792 --> 01:11:57.168
We have to move soon and fast.

396
01:11:58.169 --> 01:12:01.381
You've been the cause of every
drop of blood spilt in this place.

397
01:12:01.548 --> 01:12:04.926
But not now. Now you're gonna
be with us step by step.

398
01:12:05.093 --> 01:12:06.553
Blow for blow.

399
01:12:06.720 --> 01:12:08.054
Until this nightmare is over.

400
01:12:10.265 --> 01:12:11.600
Then what?

401
01:12:11.766 --> 01:12:13.768
We go up. We attack.

402
01:12:13.935 --> 01:12:18.023
We get who we came here for
and we use him to get out.

403
01:12:18.982 --> 01:12:20.525
Finding him won't be easy.

404
01:12:20.942 --> 01:12:22.027
The fifteenth floor.

405
01:12:23.153 --> 01:12:25.405
It's where he runs everything.

406
01:12:27.282 --> 01:12:29.534
But reaching him
is another thing entirely.

407
01:12:29.701 --> 01:12:31.453
And assuming we do get him.

408
01:12:31.620 --> 01:12:33.580
what then? What's your plan?

409
01:12:33.747 --> 01:12:35.165
We'll convince him.

410
01:12:35.624 --> 01:12:37.042
How?

411
01:12:37.208 --> 01:12:39.127
Men Change with a gun to the head.

412
01:12:39.294 --> 01:12:40.337
We don't have a gun.

413
01:12:40.503 --> 01:12:42.797
A knife. a chair leg.
your bare hands. anything.

414
01:12:42.964 --> 01:12:44.924
Just do whatever it takes
to make him ours.

415
01:12:45.091 --> 01:12:46.926
We still have time.
we can still get out.

416
01:12:53.141 --> 01:12:54.768
Who the fuck is that?

417
01:12:55.477 --> 01:12:58.229
I told him it's the wrong guy.

418
01:12:58.897 --> 01:13:02.984
He's wearing a vest. he counts. I'm not
the one who came back empty-handed.

419
01:13:04.527 --> 01:13:05.987
That's not true. is it. Andi?

420
01:13:07.530 --> 01:13:08.782
Excuse me.

421
01:13:11.576 --> 01:13:15.789
Surely you've got something to show.

422
01:13:16.539 --> 01:13:20.543
You of all people wouldn't waste
my fucking time for nothing.

423
01:13:22.253 --> 01:13:24.130
I'm sorry. I don't.

424
01:13:26.841 --> 01:13:28.593
Show me your hands.

425
01:13:32.222 --> 01:13:33.264
Bring them here.

426
01:13:33.431 --> 01:13:35.183
- What?
- Here.

427
01:13:47.112 --> 01:13:48.738
Empty.

428
01:13:49.739 --> 01:13:52.742
But I'm sure you have something.
Turn them.

429
01:14:04.421 --> 01:14:05.922
I was wrong.

430
01:14:06.089 --> 01:14:08.550
You did waste my fucking time.

431
01:14:12.262 --> 01:14:14.514
I found dead bodies.
there's a lot of them.

432
01:14:14.681 --> 01:14:16.850
Oh. yeah? What else?

433
01:14:17.016 --> 01:14:19.728
If I had to guess. I'd say there
are two more cops out there.

434
01:14:19.894 --> 01:14:21.104
Heh.

435
01:14:21.312 --> 01:14:24.065
What if I said there are three cops left.
would you agree?

436
01:14:24.232 --> 01:14:28.862
As I said. there's a lot of floors.
You could give or take.

437
01:14:29.821 --> 01:14:32.031
Give or take.

438
01:14:41.124 --> 01:14:43.168
You little prick.

439
01:14:43.877 --> 01:14:47.672
I'll admit it. I was impressed.
I really was.

440
01:14:47.839 --> 01:14:51.342
But never underestimate
the persistence of paranoia.

441
01:14:59.267 --> 01:15:02.979
After seeing that. I'd have
sat still with shit in my pants.

442
01:15:04.063 --> 01:15:08.902
Seems these monitors
are the only truth I got left.

443
01:15:09.611 --> 01:15:14.407
They never lie. they tell me
everything I need to know.

444
01:15:14.991 --> 01:15:17.368
But there's one thing
I wanted to ask.

445
01:15:17.535 --> 01:15:20.205
Why?

446
01:15:20.371 --> 01:15:23.082
Ballsy move like that.

447
01:15:24.209 --> 01:15:27.712
ain't from no clash of conscience.

448
01:15:28.338 --> 01:15:29.756
No. there's more to this.

449
01:15:31.299 --> 01:15:35.220
Then I think. it doesn't matter because
you're going to die soon anyway.

450
01:15:35.386 --> 01:15:38.348
I don't really give a shit
about "why" any more.

451
01:15:38.890 --> 01:15:41.601
No. what I want to know is

452
01:15:41.768 --> 01:15:47.065
who is this little cunt
that's been tearing my place up?

453
01:15:48.233 --> 01:15:51.444
And what would it mean for you

454
01:15:52.237 --> 01:15:56.658
if you were to die in front of him?

455
01:15:58.576 --> 01:16:01.621
Or better yet. for him to be
cut open in front of you!

456
01:16:03.998 --> 01:16:05.792
Fuck you.

457
01:16:12.257 --> 01:16:13.341
Hey!

458
01:16:21.558 --> 01:16:22.976
Hurry!

459
01:23:47.586 --> 01:23:49.130
Don't move!

460
01:23:49.297 --> 01:23:51.132
Drop the gun.

461
01:23:54.468 --> 01:23:56.304
Are we gonna play this game now?

462
01:23:56.470 --> 01:23:57.972
Get over here.

463
01:23:59.265 --> 01:24:00.975
Faster!

464
01:24:03.477 --> 01:24:05.688
Did I do something wrong. officer?

465
01:24:05.855 --> 01:24:09.108
Shut the fuck up!
Put your hands in the air!

466
01:24:12.862 --> 01:24:14.655
Dagu. tie him.

467
01:24:34.425 --> 01:24:36.927
Now you're going to get me
the fuck out of here.

468
01:24:42.350 --> 01:24:44.518
Amazing.

469
01:30:16.058 --> 01:30:17.976
Wahyu. what the hell are you doing?
Dagu?

470
01:30:18.769 --> 01:30:19.853
He didn't make it.

471
01:30:20.938 --> 01:30:24.233
Fuck. you motherfucker! Why?

472
01:30:24.400 --> 01:30:27.778
Save it. We're almost done here.

473
01:30:27.945 --> 01:30:30.823
Just one last thing to clean up.

474
01:30:30.989 --> 01:30:33.242
You'll never get out of here.
Shut up!

475
01:30:33.409 --> 01:30:36.829
Did you honestly think
it would be that easy to get in?

476
01:30:36.995 --> 01:30:39.415
Did you think we were
that fucking stupid?

477
01:30:39.581 --> 01:30:42.835
I was waiting for you.
we all were.

478
01:30:43.001 --> 01:30:45.295
Ready to pick you off one by one.

479
01:30:45.462 --> 01:30:47.881
Didn't work too well. did it?

480
01:30:48.048 --> 01:30:53.095
Oh. I don't know.
you got at least 18 dead.

481
01:30:53.262 --> 01:30:55.013
No transportation.

482
01:30:55.180 --> 01:30:57.224
You're stuck here.

483
01:31:00.436 --> 01:31:03.564
You got no one left.

484
01:31:05.107 --> 01:31:07.401
And if we're talking strength
in numbers.

485
01:31:07.568 --> 01:31:11.071
We're talking a bullet. and I
only need one for your fucking head.

486
01:31:12.573 --> 01:31:15.534
You don't get it.
you're already dead.

487
01:31:15.701 --> 01:31:18.454
You've been dead since
I got the call from Reza.

488
01:31:21.874 --> 01:31:25.669
Now I've got your attention.
It was the name. right?

489
01:31:26.962 --> 01:31:31.091
Reza and the rest of the suits have
been happy with me since day one.

490
01:31:34.094 --> 01:31:39.099
Because I know who to pay
and more importantly. how much.

491
01:31:39.266 --> 01:31:40.309
But you?

492
01:31:40.476 --> 01:31:42.686
All you are is a collector.

493
01:31:42.853 --> 01:31:44.938
It was never about replacing me.

494
01:31:45.105 --> 01:31:50.235
They sent you here to die.

495
01:31:51.445 --> 01:31:52.613
Fuck you!

496
01:31:52.780 --> 01:31:55.324
No. fuck you. big fucking man!

497
01:31:55.491 --> 01:31:59.495
You listen to me. you think
they'll let you join them at the top?

498
01:31:59.661 --> 01:32:03.540
Never! You'll always be looking up.

499
01:32:03.707 --> 01:32:08.253
You think when all this is over they'll
welcome you back and promote you.

500
01:32:08.420 --> 01:32:09.755
Make you a hero?

501
01:32:09.922 --> 01:32:11.715
Never! You fuck!

502
01:32:11.882 --> 01:32:14.301
You'll be met by someone
emptying a gun into you.

503
01:32:14.468 --> 01:32:19.097
A fucking pillow over your face
when you sleep.

504
01:32:19.264 --> 01:32:24.102
You're done. you're out.

505
01:32:24.645 --> 01:32:26.313
Asshole.

506
01:32:27.523 --> 01:32:29.358
Be quiet.

507
01:33:43.390 --> 01:33:47.895
All residents.
please return to your rooms.

508
01:33:48.478 --> 01:33:50.898
It's all over.

509
01:33:57.988 --> 01:34:00.908
He always knew that
someday someone would try to fuck him over.

510
01:34:01.825 --> 01:34:03.327
This was his insurance.

511
01:34:03.493 --> 01:34:06.955
It's evidence of every
dirty cop he ever dealt with.

512
01:34:07.789 --> 01:34:10.626
Not everyone you salute is rotten.

513
01:34:10.792 --> 01:34:12.502
Find Bunawar.

514
01:34:12.669 --> 01:34:14.379
He's a good man.

515
01:34:47.204 --> 01:34:49.247
Open the gate!

516
01:34:53.543 --> 01:34:55.253
Just keep walking.

517
01:34:55.420 --> 01:34:57.005
Follow me.

518
01:34:58.924 --> 01:35:02.094
If there's one thing I know for sure.
it's that in this world

519
01:35:03.053 --> 01:35:05.138
I can protect you.

520
01:35:06.348 --> 01:35:08.976
But can you do the same
for me in yours?

521
01:35:11.103 --> 01:35:12.437
They'll come here.

522
